snippet.title: [Favorite Horror Game #4] Best VGM 1670 - Dead Space - Welcome Aboard the USG Ishimura
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / X360 / PS3
Dead Space (2008)
Welcome Aboard the USG Ishimura
Jason Graves
